@node "Hist" "History"

@{b}08-Dec-98@{ub} - v3.4
 Heavily changed by eNTiTy:
 ∑ Substantial optimisation of most routines.
 ∑ Changed some config variable names.
 ∑ Arguments now parsed using AmigaDOS ReadArgs() instead of custom parser.
 ∑ Added -c and -t flags to FIND, which effectively make CSHOW and RAWSEND
   obsolete.
 ∑ Added -d flag to GET, do specify alternative download directory.
 ∑ Added LSITES command, to show which sites are available for the -s flag.
 ∑ Removed RAWSEND and CSHOW commands.

@{b}11-Jun-98@{ub} - v2.3
 ∑ Added proxy support via RexxKuang11.library
 ∑ Added lamer support for bad savedir config
 ∑ Added bseek.. Sends search to Open Browser via SendBrower.amirx...
 ∑ /bseek search word(s)

@{b}06-Jun-98@{ub}
 ∑ Made it work with a channel plugin....like old aminetfind.amirx
   add amihunterpub.amirx to K11 public channel plugins.
 ∑ Added output to channel command (/cshow <search text>)
 ∑†Added Raw send to users (/Rawsend <search text> <nick>)

@{b}01-Jun-98@{ub}
 ∑ Fixed what screen the GUI opens on....should open on your amirc screen.
 ∑ Added a search complete line....
 ∑ NO LONGER USES ZED_HTTP 

@{b}22-May-98@{ub}
 ∑ Given to Ariel for Public Release

@{b}25-Mar-98 - 05-May-98@{ub}
 ∑ Many Changes and fixes.....

@{b}20-Mar-98@{ub}
 ∑ First working verison....

@endnode
